---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import SectionDivider from '../components/SectionDivider.astro';
import Quote from '../components/Quote.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About — Kevin 'The General' Neal" description="The story behind the stage name. Kevin Neal is a 2× CCMA-nominated pedal steel player based in Hamilton, Ontario.">
  <Nav />

  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="section-label">// About</div>
    <h1 class="page-title">The Story Behind<br><span>The General</span></h1>
  </section>

  <section class="about-content">
    <div class="about-grid">
      <div class="about-text">
        <p class="lede">His stage name wasn't chosen. It was earned.</p>

        <p>A university-trained musician with an instinct for the spaces between notes, Kevin "The General" Neal has built one of the most respected reputations in Canadian country music &mdash; not through self-promotion, but through the undeniable authority of his playing.</p>

        <p>Based in Hamilton, Ontario, Kevin's career spans decades of live performance, studio sessions, and collaborative work with artists at every level. His primary instrument is the pedal steel guitar, though he is equally accomplished on dobro, banjo, and guitar.</p>

        <h2>On Stage</h2>
        <p>Kevin has shared stages with <strong>Darius Rucker</strong>, <strong>Midland</strong>, and some of the biggest names in North American country. His touring footprint spans three continents, with performances at landmark venues and festivals including the <strong>Grand Ole Opry</strong> in Nashville, the <strong>Calgary Stampede</strong>, <strong>Mariposa Folk Festival</strong>, and major festival stages in <strong>Norway</strong>.</p>

        <h2>In the Studio</h2>
        <p>Kevin has recorded with artists across multiple genres and continents &mdash; including appearing on <strong>Jade Eagleson's</strong> recording of <em>Steal My Girl</em>, bringing his signature tone to one of the most recognizable pop melodies of the last decade. His session work reflects the same quality that has made him a trusted first call for artists at every level.</p>

        <h2>Recognition</h2>
        <p>Twice nominated for <strong>CCMA Pedal Steel Player of the Year</strong>, Kevin's credentials come from the people who know the instrument best &mdash; fellow musicians and industry peers who recognize the rare combination of technical mastery and musical intelligence he brings to every room.</p>
      </div>

      <aside class="about-sidebar">
        <div class="sidebar-block">
          <h3>Quick Facts</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>2&times; CCMA Pedal Steel Player of the Year nominee</li>
            <li>Grand Ole Opry performance credit</li>
            <li>3 continents, countless stages</li>
            <li>University-trained, multi-instrumentalist</li>
            <li>Based in Hamilton, ON</li>
            <li>Available worldwide</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="sidebar-block">
          <h3>Instruments</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Pedal Steel (primary)</li>
            <li>Dobro / Resonator</li>
            <li>Banjo</li>
            <li>Guitar (Acoustic & Electric)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </section>

  <SectionDivider />

  <Quote
    text="His approach is systematic, tactical, and unfailingly musical. He reads a room, serves the song, and elevates the artist."
    attribution="On The General's approach"
  />
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    padding: 160px 60px 60px;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .page-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(40px, 6vw, 72px);
    font-weight: 900;
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1;
    color: var(--cream);
    margin-top: 16px;
  }

  .page-title span {
    color: var(--gold);
  }

  .about-content {
    padding: 60px 60px 100px;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.4fr 1fr;
    gap: 80px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .about-text {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 19px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--cream);
  }

  .about-text .lede {
    font-size: 26px;
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1.5;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--gold);
    padding-left: 28px;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .about-text p + p { margin-top: 24px; }

  .about-text h2 {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    letter-spacing: 4px;
    color: var(--rust);
    margin-top: 48px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .about-text :global(strong) {
    color: var(--gold);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .about-sidebar {
    position: sticky;
    top: 100px;
  }

  .sidebar-block {
    padding: 32px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(201, 168, 76, 0.15);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    background: rgba(201, 168, 76, 0.02);
  }

  .sidebar-block h3 {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .sidebar-block ul {
    list-style: none;
  }

  .sidebar-block li {
    font-family: 'Courier Prime', monospace;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--light-mid);
    padding: 8px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(201, 168, 76, 0.08);
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .sidebar-block li::before {
    content: '— ';
    color: var(--rust);
  }

  .sidebar-block li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .page-hero { padding: 120px 32px 40px; }
    .about-content { padding: 40px 32px 60px; }
    .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 48px; }
    .about-sidebar { position: static; }
  }
</style>
